# Avatar — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/avatar.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-avatar` — `display: inline-flex`, `align-items: center`, `justify-content: center`, `overflow: hidden`, `flex-shrink: 0`

### Sizes

| Class | Dimensions | Initials Font | Icon Size |
|-------|-----------|--------------|-----------|
| `.acko-avatar-xs` | 24px × 24px | 10px | var(--font-label-md-size) |
| `.acko-avatar-sm` | 32px × 32px | var(--font-label-md-size) | 16px |
| `.acko-avatar-md` | 40px × 40px | var(--font-body-sm-size) | var(--font-heading-md-size) |
| `.acko-avatar-lg` | 48px × 48px | var(--font-body-md-size) | 24px |
| `.acko-avatar-xl` | 64px × 64px | var(--font-heading-md-size) | 32px |

### Shapes

| Class | Border Radius |
|-------|--------------|
| `.acko-avatar-circle` | `--radius-full` |
| `.acko-avatar-square` | `--radius-lg` |

### Fallback
- `.acko-avatar-img` — `<img>` with `object-fit: cover`, `transition: opacity 200ms ease`
- `.acko-avatar-initials` — text centered, `font-weight: 500`, `background: --color-primary-subtle`, `color: --color-primary`
- `.acko-avatar-fallback` — fallback User icon, same bg/color as initials
